WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.325 --> 00:00:02.542
Good morning, family.

00:00:02.542 --> 00:00:03.760
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:05.693
Day 59.

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:10.674
I hope you all enjoyed the Christmas lights yesterday.

00:00:10.674 --> 00:00:12.987
We sure did; it was awesome.

00:00:13.493 --> 00:00:16.359
Walking around, Megan seemed to have a real good time.

00:00:16.750 --> 00:00:23.431
She liked to look at the ducks more than anything; she wanted those ducks to eat that popcorn so bad.

00:00:23.431 --> 00:00:32.342
We stood there for a while off-camera and tried to get those ducks to come over, but those ducks were not having it.

00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:36.605
God is so good; I love all His little creatures He's made.

00:00:37.610 --> 00:00:49.404
Like Bob Ross—he takes Peanut the pocket squirrel and has those little pigeons and all that stuff he used to carry around with him when he was painting those pictures.

00:00:49.404 --> 00:00:52.920
We loved all that; we still watch those reruns.

00:00:52.920 --> 00:01:00.440
My son used to pretend he was Bob Ross and paint pictures for me.

00:01:01.256 --> 00:01:03.942
God is good, and I just love His nature.

00:01:05.480 --> 00:01:08.485
Thank you for joining us yesterday; we appreciate it, Diana.

00:01:08.485 --> 00:01:19.835
We think it's fun and thought about doing more vlogs like that so you all can see our day and go around with us, but it's something different every once in a while.

00:01:22.848 --> 00:01:27.703
We made fun of it regarding the Bubba and the drones flying over.

00:01:28.274 --> 00:01:34.967
They don't just fly over Oklahoma; they're looking for something.

00:01:34.967 --> 00:01:39.520
Those are military; they have to be.

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:59.203
We have one of the most top-secret governments in the world, and you're telling me we have hundreds of these drones flying around and they're like, 'Well, we don't know what they are'?

00:01:59.203 --> 00:02:00.130
Baloney, y'all!

00:02:00.130 --> 00:02:03.259
They do know what they are.

00:02:03.259 --> 00:02:12.200
I told you this is something they're going to start using all the time; this is going to be a way of life for what's coming.

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:15.394
They're going to start using these drones everywhere.

00:02:15.748 --> 00:02:25.610
We don't even have the next administration in, and he's talking about shooting them out of the sky because he's not being briefed on the security all the way, it sounds like.

00:02:25.885 --> 00:02:41.986
For people to sit there and say, 'Well, I got a prophetic word,' and some people saying it's aliens—maybe I'm wrong, maybe it is, but I feel in my heart it's a desensitizing of things.

00:02:41.986 --> 00:02:56.172
We are seeing the Beast system unfolding right in front of our faces: how they're going to use technology to track you.

00:02:56.172 --> 00:03:02.993
They're just playing a poker match and bringing out their cards, showing you they have a full house.

00:03:03.620 --> 00:03:10.640
They're one-up on you, and you're still stuck on the technology from five or ten years ago.

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:19.005
They're light-years ahead of you.

00:03:19.005 --> 00:03:22.430
They've got technology that you don't have any clue about.

00:03:22.430 --> 00:03:27.060
I've told you about that pulse thing that they're going to bring out for crowd control.

00:03:27.370 --> 00:03:41.575
If they can't use firearms on people, they're just going to knock people out in the crowd, and it will look like they just passed out everywhere instead of using gas or smoke from riots.

00:03:43.040 --> 00:03:49.846
Whenever people are looting and acting nuts, they use gas and pepper spray to make the crowds obey.

00:03:56.393 --> 00:04:02.250
They'll just use this new technology, and people will fall like flies.

00:04:02.250 --> 00:04:04.700
I'm telling you, it's coming.

00:04:05.190 --> 00:04:15.624
When I went to tribulation with the Lord, all the things He showed me we're starting to see more and more on the news.

00:04:16.009 --> 00:04:19.832
You all don't realize how close we are to His coming.

00:04:19.832 --> 00:04:29.855
I told you we would start to see more signs in the heavens, and the drones are just part of the surveillance in society.

00:04:29.855 --> 00:04:34.011
They're going to start doing this in China, Europe, and the Middle East.

00:04:34.011 --> 00:04:43.560
We're going to start seeing this everywhere, and people will become more used to it instead of saying, 'Is it delivering a package?

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:52.343
' No, it's just a police drone circling and surveilling the area to make sure people are safe.

00:04:53.271 --> 00:04:54.199
Interesting.

00:04:54.199 --> 00:04:57.000
So, nothing to be alarmed about, folks.

00:04:57.000 --> 00:05:01.497
Jesus is coming; this is just part of the Beast system coming to pass.

00:05:01.829 --> 00:05:14.520
It's exciting because I know what comes next: a massive revival that's about to take place and an outpouring of finances.

00:05:16.660 --> 00:05:21.193
The Lord showed me even this yesterday.

00:05:21.193 --> 00:05:29.428
When I was driving home from the lights, the Lord said, 'Brandon, I want you to drive around for a bit; I have some things I have to talk to you about.

00:05:29.428 --> 00:05:34.760
' I told Diana, 'We can't go home yet; the Lord wants to talk.

00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:37.730
' So I just started driving and praying in the spirit.

00:05:38.587 --> 00:05:47.515
Deep groanings came in the spirit; I started interceding, and it was like a waterfall coming up out of me.

00:05:47.790 --> 00:05:56.493
Diana and the kids were just praying and interceding for what the Lord wanted to talk about.

00:05:57.706 --> 00:06:06.668
It was about what's coming with the finances; He was giving me impartation about what's coming.

00:06:09.443 --> 00:06:29.386
He told me we're not believing big enough and to enlarge our capacity in our minds to think bigger by reading His word, to believe Him for exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:06:29.386 --> 00:06:38.480
He said, 'I want you to think about that: how much can you think for over and above all that you think?

00:06:38.480 --> 00:06:41.340
' I can think some big things, folks.

00:06:41.340 --> 00:06:43.545
Can you believe God for big?

00:06:43.545 --> 00:06:49.160
You have all kinds of hopes, desires, and dreams, don't you?

00:06:51.664 --> 00:06:54.407
As a man thinks in his heart, so is he.

00:06:54.675 --> 00:07:11.093
The Lord was showing me, 'Brandon, I'm going to do even exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask me for or think.

00:07:11.093 --> 00:07:23.080
' He was talking about the thinking part because people can think big, but He said, 'Brandon, you've got to even think bigger than what you think because of what I'm about to do in this earth.

00:07:23.080 --> 00:07:27.453
' Folks, He's about to show up and show off in your life.

00:07:31.916 --> 00:07:52.479
I hear the sound of an abundance of rain, and the camels are coming, loaded down with everything you've been believing God for, everything you've stretched your hand out and sowed to believe sacrificially.

00:07:56.200 --> 00:08:01.885
Do you ever take a calculator to what you've sowed over the course?

00:08:01.885 --> 00:08:04.293
Maybe you have a record of it.

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:15.061
Even the seeds that you may have forgotten about, ask the Holy Spirit to help you remember all the things that you have sowed in the past.

00:08:15.061 --> 00:08:21.360
He said some thirty, some sixty, and some hundredfold.

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:27.022
Take a calculator and do the math on what is being laid up for you.

00:08:27.022 --> 00:08:38.352
Seedtime and harvest: seed sowing is a law, but harvest is a law just as much.

00:08:39.865 --> 00:08:46.360
The Lord told me that reaping is just as much a law as sowing.

00:08:50.479 --> 00:08:54.920
We have got to learn that it's time for us to reap.

00:08:54.920 --> 00:08:57.920
He said you will reap if you faint not.

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:01.712
But a lot of you give up on your old seed.

00:09:01.712 --> 00:09:08.325
You go, 'Well, it didn't come to pass over the last five years, so I guess that seed's dead.

00:09:08.325 --> 00:09:19.527
' I believe the Lord said the seeds you have sowed in the past will come to harvest at last.

00:09:20.183 --> 00:09:26.170
In 2025, you're going to see a multiplication of your harvest time.

00:09:26.660 --> 00:09:37.599
The sowers and the reapers are going to start going hand in hand, and as you sow, you're going to start to reap instantaneously.

00:09:37.599 --> 00:09:43.257
What you say out of your mouth and what you believe in your heart is going to start to come to pass.

00:09:43.257 --> 00:09:56.091
I believe with all my heart this is a time for you to believe big: spiritually, physically, emotionally, and mentally.

00:09:56.463 --> 00:10:00.209
You may say, 'I don't need finances; I'm rich.

00:10:00.209 --> 00:10:03.033
' Well, you may need something in your body.

00:10:03.399 --> 00:10:13.386
God is a healer, and He said, 'Beloved, I wish above all things that you prosper and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:10:13.386 --> 00:10:24.280
' Prosperity is not just about finances; it's about living in wholeness mentally, emotionally, physically, and financially.

00:10:25.360 --> 00:10:32.897
Your marriage—people go, 'I'm rich and whole in my body, but my marriage is terrible and my kids talk to me terribly.

00:10:32.897 --> 00:10:33.754
' That's not whole.

00:10:34.183 --> 00:10:43.713
He wants you to be made whole through everything abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:10:56.346 --> 00:10:56.635
I want my marriage good, my children healthy, my health good, and a good job.

00:11:07.978 --> 00:11:09.111
Do you see?

00:11:09.111 --> 00:11:11.930
He wants you to live an abundant life.

00:11:13.170 --> 00:11:25.898
The Lord told me from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, which was last October, you'll start to see first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation on that ear.

00:11:26.356 --> 00:11:37.920
The Lord told me you would start to see the glory in different levels: ankle-deep, knee-deep, waist-deep, and over the top.

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:41.591
It's time to go down to the bottom of that pool at His altar.

00:11:41.591 --> 00:11:51.530
I believe it's a time like never before that we are joint heirs of Jesus Christ and we display kingliness.

00:11:51.530 --> 00:11:56.815
We show it off so that people see that inside of us.

00:12:02.262 --> 00:12:03.329
Yes, all this stuff's going on around us, and there's a lot of drama on the news every day.

00:12:07.213 --> 00:12:17.839
But my goodness, y'all, we're about to see the glorious church rise and the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever known.

00:12:18.199 --> 00:12:24.380
It's all going to come through you, for you were called to the kingdom for such a time as this.

00:12:26.809 --> 00:12:30.610
I'm seeing people freaking out on the news, but it's just part of it.

00:12:30.610 --> 00:12:33.407
They're using the drones for surveillance; they're looking for something.

00:12:36.906 --> 00:12:43.634
It's not aliens or spooky stuff; it's technology you don't even realize they have.

00:12:43.908 --> 00:12:47.447
They're orbs and all this other stuff coming in and out of the water.

00:12:51.079 --> 00:13:01.974
We're looking at AI technology now, but they've had AI for probably twenty years and just never brought it out to the public until now.

00:13:01.974 --> 00:13:08.160
What are they hiding behind closed doors that's 'freaky out' stuff?

00:13:13.760 --> 00:13:22.090
Like the AWACS or the stealth bomber—that was a big deal, but how long did they have that before they brought it to the public?

00:13:22.090 --> 00:13:26.011
That technology is ancient compared to what they're doing now.

00:13:36.783 --> 00:13:37.257
Trust me, they've got brilliant people using technology and computers that would blow your mind.

00:13:48.971 --> 00:13:54.686
The drone is old news, but they're going to use them and it's going to become mainstream.

00:13:54.686 --> 00:13:57.759
It's going to be like the Terminator; they'll have robots out fighting battles soon.

00:14:01.253 --> 00:14:04.725
They won't even put soldiers on the field; they'll be fighting robots.

00:14:08.490 --> 00:14:11.697
Seriously, that's what I told you all we're about to see.

00:14:11.697 --> 00:14:21.806
And over Poland, I believe by Warsaw, a weapon that has never been used before on this earth—something catastrophic.

00:14:26.131 --> 00:14:31.976
We pray against it, but we will see wars, rumors of wars, plagues, and pestilence.

00:14:32.993 --> 00:14:35.820
AI technology is creating a superbug.

00:14:36.145 --> 00:14:38.400
I told you that was coming; it's still coming.

00:14:39.978 --> 00:14:47.102
When I've been interceding, things have been delayed because the Lord said, 'My people prayed in October.

00:14:47.102 --> 00:14:59.476
' As He said in His word: 'If my people who are called by my name will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways...

00:14:59.476 --> 00:15:00.889
' It's happening, folks.

00:15:06.600 --> 00:15:09.399
He is a God of His word.

00:15:09.399 --> 00:15:10.625
He stands by His covenant.

00:15:13.493 --> 00:15:18.090
Now He's watching to see what we will do with it.

00:15:18.090 --> 00:15:20.714
Will you go back into your slumber?

00:15:22.019 --> 00:15:27.915
He said, 'I'm giving you a window; what will you do with it?

00:15:27.915 --> 00:15:33.950
' I'm seeing on the other side of that window, and very dark days are coming.

00:15:43.337 --> 00:15:43.653
What will you do with this time?

00:15:45.1000 --> 00:15:55.394
I'm telling you, the rocket ship is taking off, and Trump is going to bring in a whole new system.

00:16:04.244 --> 00:16:16.079
In the dot-com era of time with Elon Musk, it will be just like then whenever they brought in the internet.

00:16:16.079 --> 00:16:19.573
When they brought in the internet, everything changed.

00:16:19.573 --> 00:16:25.940
I remember as a kid we thought it was cool just to have a Nintendo or a Sega.

00:16:25.940 --> 00:16:29.860
We had a Sega and we played those games, and boy, that was big technology then.

00:16:30.107 --> 00:16:36.032
Those little guys on the screen look so goofy now when I look back at that, but that was so cool as a kid.

00:16:36.032 --> 00:16:38.541
Boy, we wanted to play that every day we got home from school.

00:16:38.541 --> 00:16:40.377
My goodness, it was a big deal.

00:16:40.377 --> 00:16:46.933
But now we look at what they have, and then the internet came out and we didn't know what it was.

00:16:46.933 --> 00:16:51.980
So we did the AOL chat online thing; we talked to those people from all over the world.

00:16:52.520 --> 00:17:01.189
My sister would go in there and they had those chat rooms, and we thought this was the coolest thing ever because we're talking to somebody in New York.

00:17:01.199 --> 00:17:10.137
And then it became bigger and bigger, but they brought laws in and they started making the internet not like the Wild West; they made it have regulations and laws.

00:17:11.783 --> 00:17:24.009
I'm telling you, that's what they're going to do with crypto, and it will be like the dot-com era and it will explode in the days ahead.

00:17:24.378 --> 00:17:30.080
They will adopt it, and it is part of the Beast system.

00:17:30.080 --> 00:17:36.446
It will be part of the Beast system, the One World Currency, all digital.

00:17:39.378 --> 00:17:41.400
I saw the dollar fall.

00:17:41.400 --> 00:17:45.020
Remember I told you all it was like on a flagpole?

00:17:47.298 --> 00:17:56.740
I saw a $100 bill on the flagpole and I saw the purchasing power of it went to half; the dollar was only worth about fifty cents.

00:17:57.105 --> 00:18:08.919
I saw the dollar crash and I saw digital writing come on the flagpole as it started to fade out and went into digital, like crypto lines.

00:18:13.667 --> 00:18:19.839
Back then, whenever the Lord showed me this, there was not much about crypto; I didn't pay any attention to it.

00:18:19.839 --> 00:18:26.063
But it started turning into digital code moving, and that's just like crypto.

00:18:27.280 --> 00:18:36.965
I saw the dollar turn into a digital dollar and it went to a digital platform like crypto.

00:18:37.371 --> 00:18:45.799
The Lord showed me the dollars in the bank were worthless and the bank seized them.

00:18:54.406 --> 00:19:02.371
And I've warned you—this is another thing the Lord showed me—that the banks would not loan soon, that the house of cards would fall, and that you would see interest rates and everything skyrocket.

00:19:02.371 --> 00:19:05.128
Soon there would be a loaning freeze.

00:19:05.128 --> 00:19:13.960
The banks would not loan the money because of the credit and all of the debt of America.

00:19:23.320 --> 00:19:23.760
I saw banks not loaning money out on houses and cars.

00:19:39.645 --> 00:19:39.874
I'm telling you, a 1930s-style crash will come eventually; you will see this.

00:19:41.159 --> 00:19:41.759
I saw a great humbling coming.

00:19:44.360 --> 00:19:46.260
But before I saw this coming, I saw a wealth transfer.

00:19:57.088 --> 00:20:03.519
And that's why I always thought, 'Lord,' because whenever I'm seeing a part or hearing a part, I think, 'Well, it's right in front of my face; it's going to happen.

00:20:03.519 --> 00:20:11.331
' But the Lord has always shown me that there was a group of people—he calls them the Remnant.

00:20:14.020 --> 00:20:24.159
The Remnant will walk in a financial blessing and prosperity—not everybody, because he told me, 'Certain people will make it to the starting line, Brandon.

00:20:25.736 --> 00:20:40.296
They will make it to the starting line because they've listened to all the prophetic voices, but they will not run the race and make it because it's a marathon.

00:20:40.296 --> 00:21:04.651
' Because they're not listening to me, they will not be able to listen to the people on the internet for what's coming; they have to have a personal relationship with me so that they will make it through the marathon for what's coming.

00:21:15.854 --> 00:21:18.194
I saw a group of people, and it was a very small group, like half a percentage—like a 1% group—that walks in an extreme amount of wealth.

00:21:18.884 --> 00:21:34.599
I saw the megachurches that had mega loans, huge loans on their buildings; I saw them being foreclosed on because when the dollar crashes and things happen, the people will not be able to fund those megachurches.

00:21:34.599 --> 00:21:43.355
So the banks will recall those loans and foreclose on those buildings because they don't want the churches going anyway.

00:21:43.355 --> 00:21:53.713
But I saw all this stuff taking place and I saw people having revival in fields.

00:21:53.713 --> 00:21:58.347
I saw, like I told you all, 'Holy Ghost Woodstock.

00:21:58.347 --> 00:22:21.000
' I see things over the course of the last five years of what he showed me, and whenever I can put them together, you can make a picture of what he's trying to say because all of them connect like a puzzle.

00:22:21.000 --> 00:22:32.246
But he said the finances would happen first, and that's whenever I saw the Iraqi Dinar re-establishing.

00:22:44.005 --> 00:22:44.320
I saw XRP; I saw these cryptos; I saw this stuff happening first.

00:22:52.074 --> 00:22:52.406
And then I saw a wealth transfer.

00:22:52.406 --> 00:22:59.930
I saw the abundance of money come into the Body of Christ, and then I saw them distributing it and learning how to keep it so they don't lose it.

00:22:59.930 --> 00:23:02.669
And then I saw a crash.

00:23:02.669 --> 00:23:24.039
When this happens, I saw those people able to help take care of the ones that didn't have it, making sure the Gospel did not suffer, making sure the Gospel was taken care of and that God's word still got out, because it takes finances to do that.

00:23:24.039 --> 00:23:30.684
I'm telling you, the Lord's not going to lack any good thing.

00:23:46.693 --> 00:23:53.142
He knows what's coming and just like he told Joseph—I heard him say, 'Just like I took care of Joseph, Brandon, for the seven years of plentiful and seven years of famine, I'm going to do the same with you to the ones that are listening.

00:23:53.142 --> 00:24:03.437
' But see, Joseph was the only one that heard it, and he told all the others because he interpreted the dream.

00:24:03.437 --> 00:24:12.770
They brought in the stuff and then he took care of the ones that needed it.

00:24:12.770 --> 00:24:16.790
But it made them into bondage because they weren't listening for it themselves.

00:24:20.604 --> 00:24:23.460
You have to follow the voice of the Lord for your life for what's coming.

00:24:23.460 --> 00:24:33.600
It is vital that you make it through this for your family, that you hear him on what's coming.

00:24:33.600 --> 00:24:53.330
Folks, very hard days are coming for folks; some of them are going to go without, and it will be a very humbling time.

00:25:01.583 --> 00:25:02.051
People will say, for what I have seen coming, that this is an Ichabod—God is mad.

00:25:10.653 --> 00:25:11.180
But he said, 'No, it's not an Ichabod.

00:25:11.180 --> 00:25:15.039
' Do you understand?

00:25:15.039 --> 00:25:24.609
For some of the things I've seen coming, you say, 'Brandon, you told us all this was coming in 2025.

00:25:24.609 --> 00:25:29.312
' The Lord said, 'I'm giving you extended time because you prayed.

00:25:29.312 --> 00:25:35.604
' He said, 'I want not that one should perish, but all come to repentance.

00:25:35.604 --> 00:25:52.080
' But in this timeframe, because we prayed and we see Trump coming and we see him bringing in the crypto, we see him doing this—he's establishing the Beast Kingdom.

00:25:52.080 --> 00:26:00.400
It is what it is, folks; it's what's going to happen regardless of what we want to see happen.

00:26:14.280 --> 00:26:14.600
This is Bible, and we will see a One World Currency.

00:26:19.425 --> 00:26:21.020
I believe there are certain cryptos, the Five Pillars, that will be the foundation for a one currency.

00:26:21.020 --> 00:26:38.873
But it's all done by computers, and it will be done by the chips, and it will be done by satellites, and it will be done all by this weird stuff going on—drones and how they track people.

00:26:38.873 --> 00:26:47.960
So we're seeing it, and it's exciting because I know what's coming next, and Jesus is getting ready to come back for his bride.

00:26:51.605 --> 00:26:52.375
But it's not time yet; he wants a harvest.

00:26:52.375 --> 00:27:11.105
People get mad about that and say, 'Well, I hope he's coming back tomorrow,' and I'm like, 'Yes, but your cousin that's not born again is going to go through the Tribulation; they have a great opportunity to go to hell.

00:27:11.105 --> 00:27:29.199
' I'm telling you, there's a lot of people that I'm believing God for, like an Elon Musk or a Kim Kardashian or Taylor Swift or some major actor that needs Jesus Christ.

00:27:29.199 --> 00:27:33.980
If they don't get him, they're going to hell.

00:27:33.980 --> 00:27:38.845
I'm like, 'Man, what an opportunity to win the lost!

00:27:38.845 --> 00:27:51.680
What an opportunity to show them and display Jesus to these people, to lay hands on the sick and see them recover.

00:27:51.680 --> 00:28:05.213
' That we would be those people that are the salt of the earth, that they show the light like never before.

00:28:18.853 --> 00:28:19.426
So I don't know, I'm excited, y'all.

00:28:19.426 --> 00:28:40.490
I know I've talked about this before, but it needs to be talked about again and again because I know faith cometh by hearing, and it will help you to know what's coming.

00:28:40.860 --> 00:28:44.017
The drones are just part of the plan.

00:28:44.017 --> 00:28:58.743
And then we see Elon Musk talking on this video about the cure for cancer and it being held back, and that it's really there.

00:29:10.346 --> 00:29:12.924
